maps/forest/path-02.json/entities/797/se.orig: I like all these little lanterns.\. This place has a great atmosphere.
maps/forest/path-02.json/entities/797/se.text: J'aime bien ces petites lanternes.\. Cet endroit a du charme.

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/837/se.orig: Wooden arch bridge...\. Still no laser bridge.
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/837/se.text: Encore un pont en bois...\. Toujours pas de pont laser.

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.orig: Phew...\. that was a close one!
Thank you so much for the help!
Say...\. are you with the Last Minute Heroes?
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.text: Dis... Tu ne travaillerais pas pour les Héros de la Dernière Minute ?

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.orig: Hah, I knew it!\. You guys are the best!\. Thanks a bunch!
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.text: Ah, je le savais !\. Vous, vous êtes les meilleurs !\. Merci mille fois !

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.orig: Looks like you saved the day, pardner!\. Nice work!
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.text: On dirait que tu l'as sauvé à la dernière minute, partenaire !\. Bon travail !

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.orig: How about it, still got time to rescue a few more players?
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.text: Qu'en dis-tu, tu as encore du temps pour sauver quelques joueurs de plus ?

maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.orig: Just head back to the Cave Inn and wait for my call!
maps/forest/path-03.json/entities/844/se.text: Retourne juste à l'Auberge des Caves et attend mon coup de fil !
